20int GetMinBitrateBps() {
21 constexpr int kMinBitrateBps = 5000;
22 return kMinBitrateBps;
23}
24
25DataRate GetMinBitrate() {
26 return DataRate::BitsPerSec(GetMinBitrateBps());
27}
